{"lemma":"زاوِيَةُ","slug":"زاوِيَةُ","root":"ز.#.#","root_slug":"ز-_-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-_-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18457"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%88%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"angle, corner, edge"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"street corner"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cell, hermitage"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"column"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the feminine form of active participle of the verb زَوَى (zawā)."},"ipa":["/zaː.wi.ja/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18457","headword_ar":"زَاوِيَةٌ","root":"zwY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A corner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an angle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rukon","text_ar":"رُكْن"},{"kind":"text","text":",) of a house or room or the like: (K:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilapN","text_ar":"فَاعِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawaY","text_ar":"زَوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaEa","text_ar":"جَمَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because of its em-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1274},{"kind":"text","text":"bracing ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liA^an~ahaA jamaEato","text_ar":"لِاَنَّهَا جَمَعَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":") a part, or portion, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quTorFA","text_ar":"قُطْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":",) thereof: (Msb, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawaAyaA","text_ar":"زَوَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is irreg.; for by rule it should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawaA='K","text_ar":"زَوَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", being originally of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fawaAEilu","text_ar":"فَوَاعِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEaAy^ilu","text_ar":"فَعَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) They say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kamo fiY Alz~awaAyaA mina AlxabaAyaA","text_ar":"كَمْ فِى الزَّوَايَا مِنَ الخَبَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How many hidden things are there in the corners!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [In geometry,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An angle."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAwiyapu AlEaw~aA='i","text_ar":"زَاوِيَةُ العَوَّا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The star"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"γ","text_ar":"γ","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Virgo;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaw~aA='u","text_ar":"العَوَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being composed of four stars,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"γ,δ,ε","text_ar":"γ,δ,ε","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"η","text_ar":"η","orth_type":"plain"},{"kind":"text","text":"of Virgo, disposed nearly in the form of a capital L, with"},{"kind":"text","text":"ε, δ, γ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from top to bottom and"},{"kind":"text","text":"η"},{"kind":"text","text":"to the right. ] ―         -b4-  In a saying cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAwiyapN","text_ar":"رَاوِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawaAyaA","text_ar":"زَوَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Houses,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tents."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwY","text_ar":"روى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b5-  [And in the present day, the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAwiyapN","text_ar":"زَاوِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small mosque,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chapel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in some instances, a building of this kind, thus called, serves as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hospice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an asylum for poor Muslims, students and others;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribaATN","text_ar":"رِبَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["K","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}